{"id":268894,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-不服公安传唤，无锡丁红芬申请行政复议/","date":"2012-12-18T08:15:50Z","modified":"2012-12-18T08:15:50Z","title":"维权网 | 不服公安传唤，无锡丁红芬申请行政复议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，丁红芬通过挂号信向无锡市滨湖区政府递交行政复议申请书，请求依法确认无锡市公安局滨湖分局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>作出的滨公（东）自行传字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">181</span><span>号《传唤证》违法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>无锡丁红芬于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>在北京上访后，被无锡截访人员限制人身自由。当年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>关在无锡市滨湖区宝龙宾馆，后经五次转移，最后被转移到青山湾金海花园，这是军事基地，也成为关押丁红芬的黑监狱，窗户被封死，不透一丝阳光。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>无锡市地方政府雇佣一家私人保安公司，老板叫沈东华，对丁红芬实施看押。其看押人员多是地痞流氓，或者刑满释放人员，或者是闲散的家庭妇女。在黑监狱中，看管人员对丁红芬戴黒头套，扇耳光，揪头发，丁红芬稍有反抗，看管人员就把黒套塞在她嘴中，不准叫喊，并把她的双手反吊墙上，铐在老虎凳上。每天只供应一两食物，饿得丁红芬浑身无力。她终于熬过了黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>天的日日夜夜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，保安将黑头套蒙住丁红芬的眼睛，押送到东降派出所，派出所向她出示了滨公（东）自行传字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">181</span><span>号《传唤证》，以“涉嫌扰乱社会秩序”为由，对她传唤。丁红芬认为：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>首先，公安机关在作出传唤证前，已经限制受害人的人身自由，属于程序违法；其次，公安机关所谓“涉嫌扰乱社会秩序”毫无事实根据，且始终没有列举扰乱社会秩序的事实。为此，丁红芬申请行政复议，希望滨湖区政府查清事实，依法作出公正的行政复议决定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附：关押丁红芬时间和地点：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>关在无锡市滨湖区宝龙宾馆；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>1<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">至</span> 7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>24<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">关在惠山区百达饭店<span lang=\"EN-US\">；</span></span></span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>关在滨湖区中桥和平商务宾馆；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日关在青山湾金海花园；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>关在惠山区百达饭店，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>关在青山湾金海花园（军事基地）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬住：无锡市滨湖区太湖街道锡南路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">106</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}